Paper: hep-th/9710200

Date: 1997-10-27

Title: Anyon Zitterbewegung

Comments: 5 pages, Latex; email

A new model for anyon is proposed, which exhibits the classical analogue ofthe quantum phenomenon - Zitterbewegung. The model is derived from existingspinning particle model and retains the essential features of anyon in thenon-relativistic limit.